(79, 1, '2017-06-27 05:56:23', '2017-06-27 05:56:23', '<strong><b>Follow Them - Or Watch your Business Slowly Fade Away...</b></strong>\r\n\r\nRemember the good old days when the formula for success was to spend a few thousand dollars on advertising in the newspaper or direct mail, generate a bunch of leads, then send your salesmen in to close early, often, &amp; hard?\r\n\r\nEverything changed in the 2000\'s. With the recession, wireless internet and smart phones; everyone got instant access to information 24/7.\r\n\r\n<strong><b>NEW RULE #1 - Differentiate Or Die</b></strong>\r\n\r\nYouve got to instantly &amp; definitively communicate exactly why youre different &amp; better than all your competitors... then integrate online, in ads, EVERYWHERE. We call this, \"Identity.\"\r\n\r\n<strong><b>OLD RULE #1</b></strong>- Place your ads and sit back and wait for the phone to ring. As long as you spent the money, youd succeed.\r\n\r\n<strong><b>NEW RULE #2 - Turn Lookers into Buyers</b></strong>\r\n\r\nYour website will make or break your entire marketing program. Now your website has to not only look nice, it has to make your prospects FALL IN LOVE with your company. It should give compelling reasons why youre different and better, and provide evidence and social proof to back up your claims.\r\n\r\n<strong><b>OLD RULE #2</b></strong>- Just having a nice-looking website gave you enough credibility for most prospects.\r\n\r\n<strong><b>NEW RULE #3 - Search Engine Dominance</b></strong>\r\n\r\nAll of the lost leads from advertising are now on the Web, capture them or die. SEO (Search Engine Optimization) isnt optional anymore; its absolutely mandatory that you learn how to dominate.\r\n\r\n<strong><b>OLD RULE #3</b></strong>- Most of your business came from your advertising; anything the search engines brought you was gravy.\r\n\r\n<strong><b>NEW RULE #4 - Pre-Appointment Selling.</b></strong>\r\n\r\nMake prospects fall in love with your company before you ever set foot in their business. A combination of your website, emails, phone scripting, and reports will convince prospects that theyd be crazy to do business with anyone else but you, regardless of price.\r\n\r\n<strong><b>OLD RULE #4</b></strong>- Show up for sales meetings, close early, often, and hard and walk away with the sale.\r\n\r\n<strong><b>NEW RULE #5 - Show Mastery</b></strong>\r\n\r\nMMs formula will increase leads and appointments by 3 to 10 times over whatever youre doing now. The program is simple to understand, easy to implement, and predictable for increased results. Yes, PREDICTABLE RESULTS. Refreshing...\r\n\r\n<strong><b>OLD RULE #5</b></strong>- Show up at the trade show with your booth and sales people, wait for the big crowds, and set appointments.\r\n\r\n<strong><b>NEW RULE #6 - Turn One Sale Into Many</b></strong>\r\n\r\nOur Proximity marketing program is light years ahead of the old send 3 postcards and pray method. Well show you exactly what to do, step by step, to get your prospects to buy from you like its going out style.\r\n\r\n<strong><b>OLD RULE #6</b></strong>- Send a few postcards out and wait for calls to come in.\r\n\r\n<strong><b>NEW RULE #7 - Advertising</b></strong>\r\n\r\nDirect response advertising doesnt work very well anymore; advertising is now about building relationships and nurturing future buyers to fall in love with you NOW so theyll buy from you LATER.\r\n\r\n<strong><b>OLD RULE #7</b></strong>- As long as you were spending the money to buy your leads you were in good shape. Leads were predictable and cost effective.\r\n\r\n<strong><b>Conclusion</b></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><b>These are the 7 New Rules Of Marketing, follow them, or watch your business slowly fade away.</b></strong>\r\n\r\nIf you think need assistance with these new rules of marketing - without spending a ton of money - to grow your business, beyond where you think possible - schedule a zero cost 10 minute session with Brian Gibson, the small business growth expert. There\'s nothing for sale. Just seeing if we can help. Visit:<a href=\"http://www.10minutesession.com/\"><u>http://www.10MinuteSession.com</u></a>', '7 New Rules', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '7-new-rules', '', '', '2017-07-24 10:19:43', '2017-07-24 10:19:43', '', 0, 'http://webdeveloperlive.com/networkrv/?page_id=79', 0, 'page', '', 0),
