(413, 1, '2017-07-17 05:04:01', '2017-07-17 05:04:01', 'Our launch program, will give you a simple but extremely powerful way for you to gain greater control of your launch marketing RESULTS and solve several of the main sales and marketing problems you may be facing with today\'s successful product launch.\r\nYou will bridge the gap between jaded prospects and increased sales and profitability. Whether your company relies on a sales force, advertising or marketing (or a combination), you systematize your marketing so that it produces very predictable, extremely profitable results.\r\nSome of the topics covered include:\r\nHow to set the standard within your industry to ensure that prospects come to you FIRST.\r\nHow to instantly communicate your selling advantages in compelling terms.\r\nHow to increase your advertising effectiveness by up to 3,000%.\r\nHow to eliminate your competitors and monopolize the market in your industry.\r\nHow to \"franchise\" your sales system and create extraordinary results from ordinary people.\r\nThe strategies in this powerful program are applicable to manufacturing businesses. You will uncover ways to implement them into your business immediately and you will probably never find this much hands-on, useful-right-now information for FREE anywhere else.', 'Downloads', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '73-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-07-17 05:04:01', '2017-07-17 05:04:01', '', 73, 'http://webdevelopers1.com/networkrv/73-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
