(469, 1, '2017-07-18 09:51:03', '2017-07-18 09:51:03', '<strong><b>Newsletter And Email Delivery Services:</b></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.amailsender.com/\"><strong><b>AMailSender.com</b></strong></a>- Send mass emails, track their use, verify email addresses and much more.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.aweber.com/\"><strong><b>Aweber.com</b></strong></a>- Use to send unlimited automated email messages in HTML format to your target audience.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.benchmarkemail.com/\"><strong><b>BenchmarkEmail.com</b></strong></a>- Build email lists, design and test your emails for speed, use their pre-built templates and more.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://campaigner.com/\"><strong><b>Campaigner.com</b></strong></a>- Create instant, professional looking e-mail campaigns ready to be sent at anytime.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.campaignmonitor.com/\"><strong><b>CampaignMonitor.com</b></strong></a>- An application which allows web designers to manage newsletters and deliver campaigns to their subscribers.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.experian.com/\"><strong><b>CheetahMail.com</b></strong></a>- Focused and highly targeted customer email campaigns which can be measured with accuracy.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.constantcontact.com/index.jsp\"><strong><b>ConstantContact.com</b></strong></a>- Create custom made emails or choose from already existing templates. You dont need any technical knowledge, simply use the wizard and create professional looking e-mails in a few minutes.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.eneighbors.com/\"><strong><b>eNeighbors.com</b></strong></a>- Nice way to keep track of neighborhood happenings through online newsletter specifically focused on households.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://feedblitz.com/\"><strong><b>Feedblitz.com</b></strong></a>- RSS to email and blog to email. Popular service with bloggers that can also be used to deliver email newsletters through Feedburner\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://accounts.google.com/ServiceLogin?service=feedburner&amp;continue=https%3A%2F%2Ffeedburner.google.com%2Ffb%2Fa%2Fmyfeeds\"><strong><b>Feedburner.com</b></strong></a>- The popular feed management tool for tracking blog readership also supports email newsletters. Very popular with bloggers.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://friendlybriefs.com/\"><strong><b>Friendlybriefs.com</b></strong></a>- A way to interact with friends and family. Ensures tighter integration by aligning individuals with blogging and social networking in the form of a newspaper.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.getresponse.com/\"><strong><b>GetResponse.com</b></strong></a>-\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://sharpspringmail.com/\"><strong><b>Graphicmail.com</b></strong></a>- Easy way to create and send newsletters to customers. Includes a statistics feature which allows you to see who is reading your newsletter.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.heyamigo.com/\"><strong><b>HeyAmigo.net</b></strong></a>- Site owners can add this service to their newsletters; it searches for relevant ads from its database.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.icontact.com/\"><strong><b>iContact.com</b></strong></a>- A newsletter solution for email marketers as well as bloggers. Subscribers can create, publish and track their campaigns.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.hugedomains.com/domain_profile.cfm?d=inserit&amp;e=com\"><strong><b>Inserit.com</b></strong></a>- Users can embed newsletters and other live information into their web-pages or blogs.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.internetmailmanager.com/\"><strong><b>InternetMailManager.com</b></strong></a>- A self-service email marketing company that allows you to create your own opt-in lists, publish your newsletters, and send out marketing campaigns.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://letterpop.com/\"><strong><b>Letterpop.com</b></strong></a>- Users can create and send online newsletters to friends, family members, businesses and other organizations for special occasions.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://madmimi.com/\"><strong><b>MadMimi.com</b></strong></a>- Its brand of bulk email marketing provides design features that make it easy for you to create fashionable and professional emails.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.campaignmonitor.com/\"><strong><b>Mailbuild.com</b></strong></a>- A niche e-mail newsletter tool built for web designers.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://mailandgo.co.uk/\"><strong><b>Mailandgo.co.uk</b></strong></a>- Choose from many templates to create professional email newsletters for your subscribers. Features real-time reporting of the emails being read and links clicked on.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://mailchimp.com/\"><strong><b>Mailchimp.com</b></strong></a>- Users can send newsletters in HTML format which makes e-mail marketing easy.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://mail-dog.com/explore/\"><strong><b>MailDogManager.com</b></strong></a>- Use their wizard to create HTML newsletters and manage multiple email lists from one spot.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://myemma.com/\"><strong><b>MyEmma.com</b></strong></a>- Online service through which users can create email newsletters and campaigns and send them to focused user groups.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.mynewsletterbuilder.com/\"><strong><b>MyNewsletterBuilder.com</b></strong></a>- Allows you to create your own full-color newsletters. Features templates, multiple email formats, an archive of past issues and more.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://newsberry.com/\"><strong><b>Newsberry.com</b></strong></a>- Create your e-mail, send to your list and check results. Simple and easy.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://newsletterarchive.org/\"><strong><b>Newsletterarchive.org</b></strong></a>- A directory where all the newsletters and mailing lists are consolidated by the users.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://octeth.com/\"><strong><b>Octeth.com</b></strong></a>- Allows users to deliver rich email marketing campaigns via personalized newsletters to recipients.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pinpointe.com/\"><strong><b>PinPointe.com</b></strong></a>- A good email marketing solution for businesses that send only occasional emails to their contact lists every month.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://primomailer.com/\"><strong><b>Primomailer.com</b></strong></a>- Web-based tool allowing users to send email newsletters to their subscribers. Includes subscriber management and detailed statistics.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://emarketing.rspread.hk/\"><strong><b>Respread.com</b></strong></a>- Newsletter focused towards permission based e-mail marketing.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.spredfast.com/shoutlet\"><strong><b>Shoutlet.com</b></strong></a>- A new way to create newsletters allowing users extensive control over them. They can track results of newsletters for every individual, customize the HTML design and refine it to best fit requirements.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.verticalresponse.com/\"><strong><b>VerticalResponse.com</b></strong></a>- Its advanced editing features make it ideal for emails and newsletters with several pictures in them, but its email delivery isn\'t reliable for Gmail recipients.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.whatcounts.com/\"><strong><b>Whatcounts.com</b></strong></a>- Provides consulting into email marketing methods and newsletter management.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.ymlp.com/\"><strong><b>YMLP.com</b></strong></a>- Send your newsletters to mass users.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://zookoda.com/\"><strong><b>Zookoda.com</b></strong></a>- An email marketing application for bloggers. They can send periodic blog posts to their visitors via e-mail for free.\r\n\r\n<strong><b>Choosing The Best Web Hosting Service?</b></strong>\r\n\r\nTo choose the best web hosting service for your website needs you need to consider many options like, how much do you want to spend? How much space do you need? Do you need a domain? There are some top quality web hosts around who have been in the industry many years, so they can offer you a higher level of service than some web hosts who can charge nearly 3 times as much. So with web hosting you dont always get what you pay for. Try to stick with reputable companies, who you know will have the best uptime and reliability for you website. They usually can afford to offer you better deals also as they have economies of scale from hosting many hundreds of thousands of websites. Sites like Hostgator.com, eHost.com, iPage.com, BlueHost.com are website hosts you should consider.\r\n\r\nStorage space, bandwidth, free domain or not, which control panel do they use, do you get a free domain? There are so many factors you really need to research and use comparisons to see what is the best option for what you need. If you are looking for an ecommerce store, a website builder, or a WordPress blog, look at each provider to see their pros and cons.\r\n\r\nWe recommend if you are a newbie finding a host which has cPanel - Hostgator.com - as this is a very easy to use control panel, also if you dont own a domain already, go for a host which includes a free domain name. Look at customer feedback and reviews as they will report any issues with website uptime or poor technical support. Usually this is the best way to decide who is the best web hosting provider.\r\n\r\n<strong><b>10 Web Hosting Companies</b></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bluehost.in/\">Bluehost.com</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.hostgator.com/\">Hostgator.com</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.ipage.com/\">iPage.com</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.ehost.com/\">ehost.com</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.hostclear.com/\">HostClear.com</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.sitebuilder.com/\">SiteBuilder.com</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.justhost.com/\">JustHost.com</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.ideahost.com/\">IdeaHost.com</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.websitebuilder.com/\">WebsiteBuilder.com</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.cloudhosted.com/\">CloudHosted.com</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Useful Links', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '75-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-07-18 09:51:03', '2017-07-18 09:51:03', 