(781, 1, '2017-08-08 12:55:03', '2017-08-08 12:55:03', 'The guests this week are from Camp Anytime, a new company with roots to the hotel industry that is entering the outdoor hospitality industry to provide management assistance to campgrounds and RV parks.\r\n\r\nBen Seidel is the CEO and president of Camp Anytime, and he is joined by Jarratt Watkins, who is the managing director.\r\n\r\nThe company offers a variety of solutions to owners and investors that improve sales, reduce costs, optimize efficiencies and increase return on investment.\r\n\r\nCamp Anytime supports campgrounds in five key areas. They include operations, revenue optimization, accounting, human resources and sales and marketing.\r\n\r\nSeidel and Watkins come on to the show to explain how Camp Anytime can help campgrounds of any size from larger parks that are looking for an outside management company, to mom-and-pop RV parks looking for help to save money and provide more value to customers.\r\n\r\nThe service offered go far beyond just setting up a website to accept online reservations, it includes identifying areas where growth can occur, expenses that can be reduced and services or amenities that can be added.\r\n\r\nFor more information about Camp Anytime, visit www.campanytime.com, call 443-275-5468 or email info@campanytime.com.', 'Podcast 145 features Camp Anytime executives', '(July 21, 2017) -- The guests this week are from Camp Anytime, a new company with roots to the hotel industry that is entering the outdoor hospitality industry to provide management assistance to campgrounds and RV parks. Camp Anytime supports campgrounds in five key areas. They include operations, revenue optimization, accounting, human resources and sales and marketing. The service offered go far beyond just setting up a website to accept online reservations, it includes identifying areas where growth can occur, expenses that can be reduced and services or amenities that can be added.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'podcast-145-features-camp-anytime-executives', '', '', '2017-08-08 13:31:38', '2017-08-08 13:31:38', '', 0, 'http://webdevelopers1.com/networkrv/?post_type=podcast&#038;p=781', 0, 'podcast', '', 0),
